properties.headline: FLOODING - GLENUGIE Pacific Highway
properties.otherAdvice:
There is no access to the NSW far north coast or Queensland via the Pacific Hwy.

Local traffic can currently access areas such as Tyndale, Maclean and Woodburn but motorists are being stopped at Wardell.

Motorists can use the New England Hwy instead, or divert off the Pacific Hwy at Glenugie and continue their journey all the way into Queensland via Summerland Way.
